Example usage:\nmatrix = (\n    (1, 2, 3),\n    (4, 5, 6),\n    (1, 2, 3),  # \
similar row\n    (7, 8, 9),\n    (4, 5, 6)   # similar row\n)\n\n\
unique_matrix = remove_similar_rows(matrix)\nprint(unique_matrix)\n```\n\n### \
