skips - 3 = 16 - 3 = 13 skips\\n\\n3. **Third Round:**\\n   - Sam: 16 \
skips\\n   - Jeff: Sam's skips + 4 = 16 + 4 = 20 skips\\n\\n4. **Fourth \
Round:**\\n   - Sam: 16 skips\\n   - Jeff: Half of Sam's skips = 16 / 2 = 8 \
skips\\n\\nNow, let's summarize Jeff's skips for each round:\\n- First Round: \
15 skips\\n- Second Round: 13 skips\\n- Third Round: 20 skips\\n- Fourth \
