              StyleBox["\"Response:\"", Bold, StripOnInput -> False], 
              "\"Let's denote the weight lost by the first person as \\\\( \
W_1 = 27 \\\\) kg.\\n\\nThe second person lost 7 kg less than the first, \
so:\\n\\\\[\\nW_2 = W_1 - 7 = 27 - 7 = 20 \\\\text{ kg}\\n\\\\]\\n\\nNow, let \
\\\\( W_3 \\\\) and \\\\( W_4 \\\\) be the weights lost by the two remaining \
people, who lost the same amount:\\n\\\\[\\nW_3 = W_4 = x\\n\\\\]\\n\\nThe \
