\\nDividing both sides by 2:\\n\\\\[\\nx = 28\\n\\\\]\\n\\nThus, each of the \
last two people lost:\\n\\\\[\\n\\\\boxed{28} \\\\text{ kg}\\n\\\\]\""}}, 
