the combined total number of cups of water, flour, and teaspoons of salt that \
Kimber needs to make the pizza is:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n\\\\frac{157}{6} \\\\text{ \
cups} \\\\text{ or } 26 \\\\frac{1}{6} \\\\text{ cups}\\n\\\\]\""}}, 
