years. Therefore, we can set up the equation:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n7x = \
847\\n\\\\]\\n\\nTo find \\\\( x \\\\), we divide both sides by 7:\\n\\n\\\\[\
\\nx = \\\\frac{847}{7} = 121\\n\\\\]\\n\\nThus, the number of people on the \
